 invalid}} (Tsukahara Kofun in Yamaga) - Part of the Iwahara Kofun Group in [[:en:Yamaga, Kumamoto|Yamaga, Kumamoto]], Kumamoto. Consists of nine circular Kofuns designated as a National Historic Site. Nearby are the Iwahara Horizontal Burial Chambers, a prefectural historic site.
